import lightgbm as lgb
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
from hyperopt import fmin, tpe, hp
import ipynb.fs.full.utils as utils
import ipynb.fs.full.features as fts
from sklearn.decomposition import PCA


df_train = pd.read_csv('./data/train.csv')
df_train = fts.llenar_nulls(df_train)

def full_display(df):
    with pd.option_context('display.max_rows', None, 'display.max_columns', None): 
        display(df)
        
def graficar_2d(df, features):
    '''Dado un dataframe y sus features, devuelve un dataframe de dos features e imprime
    un scatterplot con esta reduccion de dimension'''
    pca = PCA(2)

    train_red = pca.fit_transform(utils.filtrar_features(df, features))
    df_red = pd.DataFrame(train_red, columns=['x', 'y'])

    df_red.plot.scatter('x', 'y', grid=True, figsize=(13, 13))
    return df_red
